 x = 0.042424242\ldots = 0.0\overline{42}. 
100x = 4.2424242\ldots = 4.2\overline{42}
 99x = 100x - x = 4.2424242\ldots - 0.042424242 = 4.2. 
 x = \frac{4.2}{99} = \frac{42}{990}. 
3.1424242\ldots = 3.1 + x = \ldots
3.1424242\ldots=3.1+{42\over 10^3}+{42\over 10^5}+{42\over 10^7}+\cdots
=3.1+{42\over 10^3}\Bigl(1+{1\over 100}+{1\over 100^2}+{1\over 100^3}+\cdots \Bigr)
=3.1+{42\over 10^3}{1\over 1-{1\over 100}}=3.1+{42\over 990}
